<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Od" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Od,</orth> corruption of <emph>God</emph>: <cit><quote>od's blessed will,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.273" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 273</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 64</bibl></cit> (Dr. Caius' speech). <cit><quote>od's heartlings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.59" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 59</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's nouns,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 25</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's my little life,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.43" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 5, 43</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's my will,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's lifelings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 5.187" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 187</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>od's pity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 75</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>why</emph>). <cit><quote>od's pittikins,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.293" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 293</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>